quran[82]{c,v,t}:
  100,9,To kya woh us waqt ko nahin janta jab qabron mein jo kuch (madfun) hai usey nikal liya jayega
  100,10,Aur seeno mein jo kuch (makhfi) hai usey baramad karke uski jaanch padtal ki jayegi
  100,11,Yaqeenan unka Rubb us roz unse khoob bakhabar hoga
  101,1,Azeem hadisa
  101,2,Kya hai woh azeem hadisa
  101,3,Tum kya jano ke woh azeem hadisa kya hai
  101,4,woh din jab log bhikre huey parwano ki tarah
  101,5,Aur pahad rang bi rangi dhunki hui oon ke tarah hongey
  101,6,Phir jiske palade bhari hongey
  101,7,Woh dil pasand aish mei hoga
  101,8,Aur jis kay palade halke hongey
  101,9,Uski jaye qarar gehri khayi hogi
  101,10,Aur tumhein kya khabar kay woh kya cheez hai
  101,11,Bhadakti hui Aag
  102,1,Tum logon ko zyada se zyada aur ek dusre se badh kar duniya hasil karne ki dhun ne gaflat mei daal rakha hai
  102,2,Yahan tak ke (isi fikr mei) tum lab-e-gaur tak pahunch jatey ho
  102,3,"Hargiz nahin, ankareeb tumko maloom ho jayega"
  102,4,"phir (sunlo kay) hargiz nahin, ankarib tumko maloom ho jayega"
  102,5,Hargiz nahin agar tum yaqeeni ilm ki haisiyat se (is rawish ke anjam ko) jantey hotey (to tumhara yeh tarze amal na hota)
  102,6,Tum dozakh dekh kar rahogey
  102,7,Phir (sun lo ke) tum bilkul yaqeen kay saath usey dekh logey
  102,8,Phir zaroor us roz tum se in neyamaton kay barey mein jawab talabi ki jayegi
  103,1,Zamane ki qasam
  103,2,Insan dar haqeeqat badey khasarey(nuksaan) mein hai
  103,3,Siwaye un logon ke jo iman laye aur neik aamal karte rahe aur ek dusrey ko haqq ki nasihat aur sabr ki talqeen karte rahe
  104,1,Tabahi hai har us shaks ke liye jo (moonh dar moonh) logon par taan aur (peeth peechey) buraiyan karne ka khugar hai
  104,2,Jisne maal jama kiya aur usey gin gin kar rakkha
  104,3,Woh samajhta hai ke us ka maal hamesha uske paas rahega
  104,4,"Hargiz nahin, woh shaks to chakna-chur kar dene wali jagah mein phenk diya jayega"
  104,5,Aur tum kya jano ke kya hai woh chakna-chur kar dene wali jagah
  104,6,Allah ki aag khoob bhadkayi hui
  104,7,Jo dilon tak pahunchey gi
  104,8,Woh un par dhaank kar bandh kar di jayegi
  104,9,(Is halat mei ke woh) unchey unchey sutuno mei (ghirey huey hongey)
  105,1,Tumne dekha nahin ke tumhare Rubb ne haathi walon ke saath kya kiya
  105,2,Kya usne unki tadbir ko akarat nahin kar diya
  105,3,Aur un par parindo ke jhund ke jhund bhej diye
  105,4,Jo un par pakey huey mitti ke patthar phenk rahey thay
  105,5,Phir un ka yeh haal kar diya jaise janwaron ka khaya hua bhoosa
  106,1,Chunke Quresh manoos huey
  106,2,(yani) Jaadey(winter) aur garmi ke safaron se manoos
  106,3,Lihaza un ko chahiye ke is ghar ke Rubb ki ibadat karein
  106,4,Jisne unhein bhook se bacha kar khane ko diya aur khauf se bacha kar aman ata kiya
  107,1,Tum ne dekha us shaks ko jo aakhirat ki jaza va saza ko jhutlata hai
  107,2,Wahi to hai jo yateem ko dhakkey deta hai
  107,3,Aur miskeen ka khana dene par nahin uksata
  107,4,Phir tabahi hai un namaz padhne walon ke liye
  107,5,Jo apni namaz se gaflat barat-tey hain
  107,6,Jo riya-kaari(dikhawa) karte hai
  107,7,Aur maamuli zarurat ki cheezen (logon ko) dene se gurez karte hai
  108,1,(Aey Nabi ) Hum ne tumhein kausar ata kar diya
  108,2,Pas tum apne Rubb hi ke liye namaz padho aur qurbani karo
  108,3,Tumhara dushman hi jadh-kata hai
  109,1,Kehdo ke aey kafiron
  109,2,Main unki ibadat nahin karta jinki ibadat tum karte ho
  109,3,Aur na tum uski ibadat karne wale ho jiski ibadat mai karta hoon
  109,4,Aur na mai unki ibadat karne wala hoon jinki ibadat tum ne ki hai
  109,5,Aur na tum uski ibadat karne waley ho jiski ibadat main karta hoon
  109,6,Tumhare liye tumhara deen hai aur mere liye mera deen
  110,1,Jab Allah ki madad aa jaye aur fatah naseeb ho jaye
  110,2,Aur (aey Nabi s.a.s) tum dekh lo ke log fauj dar fauj Allah ke deen mein dakhil ho rahey hain
  110,3,To apne Rubb ki hamd ke saath uski tasbeeh karo Aur us se magfirat ki duaa maango. Beshak woh bada tauba qabool karne wala hai
  111,1,Toot gaye Abu Lahab ke haath aur na-murad ho gaya woh
  111,2,Uska maal aur jo kuch us ne kamaya woh uske kisi kaam na aaya
  111,3,Zaroor woh shola zan Aag mei dala jayega
  111,4,Aur (us ke saath) us ki joru(wife) bhi lagai bujhai karne wali
  111,5,Us ki gardan(neck) mein moonj ki rassi hogi
  112,1,"Kaho woh Allah hai, Yakta"
  112,2,Allah sab se bay-niyaz hai aur sab us kay mohtaj hain
  112,3,Na uski koi aulad hai aur na woh kisi ki aulad
  112,4,Aur koi uska humsar nahin hai
  113,1,Kaho main panaah maangta hoon subah ke Rubb ki
  113,2,Har us cheez ke shar se jo usne paida ki hai
  113,3,Aur raat ki tareeki ke sharr se jab ke woh chaa jaye
  113,4,Aur girhon mein phoonkne walon (ya waliyon) ke sharr se
  113,5,Aur hasid(envies) ke sharr se jab ke woh hasad(envy) karey
  114,1,"Kaho, main panah maangta hoon insano ke Rubb"
  114,2,Insano ke badshah
  114,3,Insano ke hakiki maabood ki
  114,4,us waswasa dalne wale ke shar se jo baar baar palat kar aata hai
  114,5,Jo logon ke dilon mei waswasey daalta hai
  114,6,khwah woh jinno mein se ho ya Insano mein se